title: Week 1 NFL Extravaganza
description:
The guys break down all the latest from the NFL's Opening weekend: Trouble in Dallas, Tom Brady rides on, No Cheetah, No Problem for Mahomes, and an ugly loss for Rodgers and the Packers. Plus - a culture change in New York, another big Lions (moral) victory! All that, and more.
